#. type: Content of: <guide><abstract>
#: en/gentoo-x86+raid+lvm2-quickinstall.xml:22
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"The Quick Install guide covers the Gentoo install process in a non-verbose\n"
"manner. Its purpose is to allow users to perform a stage3 install with software\n"
"RAID and LVM2 in no time. Users should already have prior experience with\n"
"installing Gentoo Linux if they want to follow this guide.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <guide><chapter><title>
#: en/gentoo-x86+raid+lvm2-quickinstall.xml:36
#, no-wrap
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <guide><chapter><section><body><p>
#: en/gentoo-x86+raid+lvm2-quickinstall.xml:41
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"This guide contains all commands you should use to complete a stage3\n"
"installation including LVM2 on top of software RAID. This guide is targeted at\n"
"experienced users. You need a connection to the Internet to download the stage3\n"
"and Portage snapshots.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <guide><chapter><section><body><impo>
#: en/gentoo-x86+raid+lvm2-quickinstall.xml:48
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"New users should read the <uri link=\"/doc/en/handbook/index.xml\">Handbook</uri>\n"
"as it gives a better overview about the installation process. The Quick Install\n"
"guide is designed for experienced users who just need a checklist to follow.\n"
msgstr ""

