#. type: Content of: <guide><chapter><section><body><p>
#: en/gentoo-x86+raid+lvm2-quickinstall.xml:181
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Then create the RAID device nodes and devices. Please bear in mind that, if you\n"
"are not using an initramfs to help during boot (which is mandatory if you use a\n"
"separate <path>/usr</path> partition as our example shows), the\n"
"<c>/boot</c> and <c>/</c> mount points should use an older metadata format which\n"
"can be specified by the <c>--metadata=0.90</c> flag:\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Attribute 'caption' of: <guide><chapter><section><body><pre>
#: en/gentoo-x86+raid+lvm2-quickinstall.xml:188
#, no-wrap
msgid "Create device nodes and devices"
